nodes.title: CLIP Text Encode (Positive Prompt)
widgets_values:
A beautiful young woman in a mint-green sleeveless cheongsam (qipao) stands in a traditional Chinese garden, framed by a circular moon gate. White flower petals fall gently through the air. The scene transitions from elegant poise to a swift, high-energy martial arts sequence using her folding fan.

Beat 1 (0-1.5s): She snaps the folding fan open with a sharp, audible flick; she immediately launches into a low, sweeping crouch, her silken dress shimmering as she spins 360 degrees on one heel. Beat 2 (1.5-2.0s): From the crouch, she spring-leaps forward through the moon gate, her body horizontal in the air for a brief moment as she executes a mid-air fan strike. Beat 3 (2.0-3.0s): Upon landing, she performs a rapid series of "butterfly kicks," her legs creating powerful arcs in the air while the falling petals are caught in the turbulence of her movement. Beat 4 (3.0-4.0s): She executes a high-speed vertical dash up the side of the stone moon gate, using three quick steps on the masonry before backflipping gracefully into the center of the frame. Beat 5 (4.0-5.0s): She lands in a perfect hero pose, snapped her fan shut across her lower face, her eyes sharp and focused, as the disturbed petals swirl around her and slowly begin to settle.

Camera work: Dynamic 360-degree orbital tracking shot that begins wide, zooms in rapidly during the mid-air leap (Beat 2), and uses a low-angle heroic tilt for the final landing (Beat 5). Acting style: Acting should be fierce, focused, and physically powerful, blending traditional elegance with martial intensity.

Technical Specs: 4K details, natural color, cinematic lighting and shadows, crisp textures, clean edges, fine material detail, high microcontrast, realistic shading, accurate tone mapping, smooth gradients, realistic highlights, detailed fabric and hair, sharp and natural.
